      "content": "That's a great start, really captures the tone. To make the character even more complex, could you expand on his logic? Like, when he's talking about why they *need* this structure, does he mention the specific characteristics or the 'natural state' of the tribesmen that makes them unable to govern themselves? I want to show his belief that it's a biological or inherent necessity.",
